CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 3, 1962, pg. 16 reads: "No Time To Waste - Within one week, a committee of the Youth Division of the NAACP, has laid plans for a voter registration drive...The right photos shows the group visiting Mr. Alton's office Tuesday to have him add another day to Hill District Registration time. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: NAACP voter registration team members, possibly including Dorothy Williams wearing beret second from left, gathered around Mr. Alton second from right, behind desk with documents, in office with architectural painting
